        jTextArea1.setLineWrap(true);
        jTextArea1.setRows(5);
        jTextArea1.setText("Terms & Conditions\nThere are certain rules and regulations one has to follow to ensure optimum safety and enjoyment at both the parks – EsselWorld and Water Kingdom. Following are the rules are to be observed and adhered:\nSr. Citizens need to carry valid age proof photo ID to avail the benefit.\nSpecial rates apply only for New Year Eve event and for special events.\nPark entry ticket prices are subject to change without prior notice.\nCharges for F&B, Riki’s Rocking Alley, Arctic Circle and other specified attractions are in addition to normal entry ticket rate, hence called paid attractions.\nNylon or lycra swimwear is mandatory for Water Kingdom. Cotton clothes are not advisable. Swimwear is also available on rent and for purchase at Water Kingdom\nBaggage facility at EsselWorld & Lockers facility at Water Kingdom is provided at nominal rates\nPatrons using various rides / slides and other facilities at EsselWorld / Water Kingdom will do so with due caution taking note of the various warning notices displayed at appropriate places and shall utilise the facilities/rides at their own risks.\nAll bags, backpacks & personal items will be inspected prior to entering the parks.\nPicnic lunches, large duffle bags, suitcases, coolers, bags with wheels, weapons, outside food & beverages, alcohol, illegal drugs (BIG NO!) strictly not allowed within premises.\nThe management shall not owe any responsibility for lost valuables, mishap or any other damages.\nIf you are driving to our parks, we recommend you leave back unessential articles and secure valuables in your car trunk.\nAll the rides are upto the extent possible are being kept fully operational. However sometimes it may happen that due to technical reasons certain rides may be non-operational and the management does not owe any liability towards it and is not answerable for such situations\nGuests are informed that we may photograph /videograph, record or reproduce the images and/or voice during their visit to our parks. Such photographs/video recordings may be used for promotional purposes for which no payment will be made to any such person.\nRights of admission reserved.\nPlease carry the printout of the E-Ticket and exchange it for a valid ticket at our parks.\nIn case of Credit / Debit Card payments, it is also MANDATORY to carry the same card from which booking was made.\nTickets once booked cannot be exchanged, cancelled or refunded.\nIn-case of non-availability of a paid attraction (game) due to technical or any other reasons, a substitute game will be provided. No cash refund in such cases. All game rules apply.\nNo two promotions/ offers can be clubbed or combined.\nPrices are standard for Child, Adult or Sr. Citizens.\nCar Combo service can be availed from morning to midnight. Additional charges applicable post midnight.\nPrices are inclusive of entry ticket to EsselWorld OR Water Kingdom (single park entry visit).\nAll Car Combo bookings and confirmations are subject to availability.\nPrices are inclusive of transfer from single pick-up point to our parks and back along with driver allowance, toll & car park charges.\nThere will be no refund on cancellations. Re-scheduling subject to prior 48 hours intimation.\nRates & terms are subject to change, without prior notice.\nAll booking terms & conditions of EsselWorld Leisure Pvt Ltd. & First Cars will apply.\nThere will be single pick-up point as confirmed at the time of booking. Multiple pick-ups points are not allowed.\nThe driver details will be sent and emailed to the guest in the night at 23:00 Hrs. for the next day bookings.\nFor reservations related queries - 24x7 CRS no. 022-40774277 / 8655433660.\nFor Car & driver details related queries - 24x7 Mumbai operations desk can be reached on 9004555345 / 8655433770.\nBy using the website to book tickets and all other products listed, the customer agrees to all terms and conditions mentioned above.");
